    <item>
      <title>投资者担心国会大选结果将解除哈里斯或特朗普的束缚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/investors-wary-of-congress-sweep-that-unshackles-harris-or-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国聚焦于僵持不下的总统竞选，国债投资者也在关注国会之争——昂贵的竞选承诺要么被控制，要么被批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/investors-wary-of-congress-sweep-that-unshackles-harris-or-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国律师请求法庭阻止前总理他信的干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/thai-lawyer-asks-court-to-stop-ex-pm-thaksin-s-alleged-meddling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名激进律师向最高法院提交了一份诉状，指控前总理他信·西那瓦和执政党为泰党破坏泰国君主制和政治制度，这增加了执政联盟稳定性面临进一步挑战的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/thai-lawyer-asks-court-to-stop-ex-pm-thaksin-s-alleged-meddling</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 09:32:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求克制，以色列誓言对伊朗发动“致命”打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-sway-over-netanyahu-tested-as-israel-vows-deadly-iran-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登一个多月来首次与本杰明·内塔尼亚胡通话，让人们注意到他在影响以色列总理对伊朗可能采取的紧急打击行动方面的能力有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-sway-over-netanyahu-tested-as-israel-vows-deadly-iran-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国借贷计划为一度夭折的项目注入新活力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-s-borrowing-plans-breath-new-life-into-once-dead-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国内阁大臣们再次讨论重大基础设施项目，包括一些被上届政府放弃的项目，这再次表明财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯正准备调整该国的财政规则，以允许更多投资借贷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-s-borrowing-plans-breath-new-life-into-once-dead-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 18:09:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布朗大学拒绝学生的反以色列提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/brown-university-board-rejects-students-anti-israel-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布朗大学投票否决了一个学生团体的提议，该提议要求其 72 亿美元的捐赠基金中排除与以色列相关的资产，该团体认为通过捐赠基金承担政治立场违背了大学的核心使命。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/brown-university-board-rejects-students-anti-israel-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 17:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
